        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You assert your power over the target's own spirit as you reach deep into its soul in order to discover a moment of excruciating anguish, debilitating humiliation, or abject despair. The target takes 12d8 spirit damage and must attempt a Will save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The target takes no damage, with a brief sensation of pain followed by a pleasant memory.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The target takes half damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The target takes full damage and is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target takes double damage and is frightened 2 and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Off-Guard] for 1 round.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d8.</p>"
